{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-b3d49d15-bf2b-40d1-ba9b-c2675dfb2deb-19\nfc_ccf43712-84c7-99d8-85ca-333f4b634f17_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","offset":440,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"3. StoryCard 上挂 `schedule_recurring_call` → `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_IN_STORY` error。\n4. 画布把卡改成 `cardKind=schedule` 仍写回**本包** `cards/`（剧情节点）；日常调度卡必须走 schedule-cards 专用创建口，不得只靠改 cardKind「伪装」。\n\n详见 [19 §3.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[08](./08-内容校验规则.md) SCHEDULE_*。\n\n## 9. Outcome（通话结果，供条件使用）\n\n```ts\ntype OutcomeFlag =\n  | \"answered_completed\"    // 正常接通并结束\n  | \"missed\"                // 未接\n  | \"busy\"                  // 占线\n  | \"hangup_early\"          // 提前挂断\n  | \"playback_completed\"    // 过场播放完成\n  | \"playback_skipped\"\n  | \"user_redial_pressed\"   // 用户按重播（作为独立模拟事件时）\n  | \"voicemail_listened\"\n  | \"callback_fired\"        // 调度的回拨已触发\n  | \"timeout\"\n\ninterface Outcome {\n  flags: Partial<Record<OutcomeFlag, boolean>>\n  completedBeats: string[]\n  missedRequiredBeats: string[]\n  /** 预留；v1 可空 */\n  narrativeVariableDelta?: Record<string, number>\n}\n```\n\nv1 由调试器 UI 构造 Outcome；引擎只消费结构化 Outcome，不关心它来自人工还是未来的 LLM Evaluator。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":470,"fileSize":19662,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":440,"endLine":470},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-b3d49d15-bf2b-40d1-ba9b-c2675dfb2deb-19\nfc_ccf43712-84c7-99d8-85ca-333f4b634f17_3","startedAtMs":"1784787528172","completedAtMs":"1784787528380"},"model_call_id":"29b43def-9d1d-4480-b70e-3d2ac632d2e0-4-n5jm","session_id":"8b776d0f-eac0-4b70-ba56-0537fbc269ba","timestamp_ms":1784787528339}
