{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-b3d49d15-bf2b-40d1-ba9b-c2675dfb2deb-20\nfc_ccf43712-84c7-99d8-85ca-333f4b634f17_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","offset":70,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"   - 无匹配 pending：使用该角色 **FreeCallCard**（Session.`packageId = \"__free__\"`）。\n5. 若该角色已有 `active` 且未结束：冲突（占线）。\n6. ActiveStoryLock：按 [19 §8.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) 决策表（soft/hard × blockedPolicy）。\n\n### 3.3 输出\n\n```ts\ninterface ResolveResult {\n  instance: CallCardInstance\n  definition: CallCardDefinition\n  source: \"story_pending\" | \"free\" | \"redial\" | \"simulate\" | \"mailbox\"\n}\n```\n\n## 4. 会话期行为（逻辑）\n\n| interactionMode | 引擎关注点 |\n|-----------------|------------|\n| `realtime_dialogue` | Composer + toolPolicy；经 DialogueAdapter 会话；等待结束 + Outcome |\n| `playback_only` | 等待 `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` / `hangup_early` / `missed` |\n| `hybrid` | 先播放阶段，再进入对话阶段 |\n\n通道（Realtime/文本/Manual）由 Adapter 决定，见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)。\n\n## 5. Outcome 构造\n\n见 [01 §9](./01-CallCard数据模型.md)。v1 由调试器 / ManualEvaluator 填写；须符合同一 Outcome schema。\n\n建议辅助计算：`missedRequiredBeats = requiredBeats - completedBeats`。\n## 6. ExitSelector","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":278,"fileSize":13582,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","readRange":{"startLine":70,"endLine":99},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-b3d49d15-bf2b-40d1-ba9b-c2675dfb2deb-20\nfc_ccf43712-84c7-99d8-85ca-333f4b634f17_4","startedAtMs":"1784787528507","completedAtMs":"1784787528946"},"model_call_id":"29b43def-9d1d-4480-b70e-3d2ac632d2e0-4-n5jm","session_id":"8b776d0f-eac0-4b70-ba56-0537fbc269ba","timestamp_ms":1784787528910}
